{"id": "1505611406966526023", "channel_id": "1173463482503536711", "type": 0, "author_id": "977903961694674974", "author_name": "navirecorbeau", "author_bot": false, "content": "Her name is indeed 伊芙/Eve! Yes, this part of the story does get a bit confusing, because Eve wasn't mentioned before or after this...\n\nI went and asked our writers about this to help clear up the confusion!\n\nAccording to our lead narrative designer:\n\nEve is one of the current \"Divus\" figures in the Church of the Lightbearers. The church's leader is Juliette (\"Lady Lantern\").\n\nThe Church has been conducting human experiments to create Awakener twins, referred to as \"Twin Divi\" (Divi=plural for Divus) to spread Dissolution.\n\nTheir known projects include:\n\nHelot & Lily, Ramona & Tawil, and Pollux & Castor. Pollux & Castor's story was covered in Beyond the Skies: I & II. It happened before Main Story started timeline wise.\n\nThe current acting Divus is Eve. She has a twin sister (name not disclosed yet).\n\nWe haven't gotten around to write more about Eve yet, but we hope we'll be able to do so!", "timestamp": "2026-05-17T16:42:12.328000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
